Email triage automation significantly boosts productivity by streamlining the management of incoming messages. By employing AI-driven tools, organizations can ensure that emails are categorized, prioritized, and responded to in a timely manner, reducing the time spent on manual sorting. This automation allows team members to focus on high-value tasks rather than getting bogged down in their inboxes.

Research indicates that employees spend an average of 28% of their workweek managing email, which can detract from more critical responsibilities. With automated triage, the process becomes more efficient, leading to:

